I am currently refining the narrative of Kael's descent with the Frost Lilies. My focus is on the transformation into Aurora Moths and how this celestial gift from Elara organically extends the established story, bringing starlight to the mortal realm. I am exploring the visual and symbolic impact of this metamorphosis.


